@(1-11=c40829.B.1) The mistress ……. She stepped forward to her own mother, and stood …… expert in song: (@wDN{Ningal} speaks:) @q[Ningal,Inana]{“He will be just like ……. He will be just like ……. He will be just like …… for you. He will be just like your father. He will be just like your mother. His mother too will …… just like your mother! His father too will …… just like your father!” (@wDN{Dumuzid} speaks:) @q[Dumuzid,Inana]{“Open the house, my lady! Open the house!”

@(12-23=c40829.B.12) At her mother's bidding, @wDN{Inana} bathed in water and anointed herself with sweet oil. She covered her body with a grand robe; she also took her pin. She straightened the lapis lazuli stones on her neck, and grasped her cylinder seal in her hand. The young lady stepped forward as @wDN{Dumuzid} pushed open the door, and like a moonbeam she came forth to him from the house. He looked at her and rejoiced in her; he embraced her and kissed her.
